# This app is a member of the pnpm workspace rooted at web/ (web/pnpm-workspace.yaml).
# The single authoritative lockfile is web/pnpm-lock.yaml. A per-app
# pnpm-lock.yaml here is a stray artifact (created when pnpm is run without
# resolving the workspace) and must NOT be committed — it drifts out of sync
# with package.json and is ignored by CI (lt-4.yml installs from web/ against
# web/pnpm-lock.yaml). See the deletion in this commit's history.
pnpm-lock.yaml
